      <title>中国支持的开发商在扩大的土地持有方面集会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/china-s-state-backed-developers-rally-on-expanded-land-holdings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国最后一家站立的房地产公司正在享受股票反弹，这是对市场份额合并的期望，因为它们在核心城市增加了土地购买。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/china-s-state-backed-developers-rally-on-expanded-land-holdings</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
